name: Dumble
info: Hold Dumbbells in your hands with the palms facing each other. Pull your right hand toward your rib cage as you rotate to the right.

name: Burbell
info: Hold Burbells in your hands with the palms facing each other. Pull your right hand toward your rib cage as you rotate to the right.

name: Dumble Rack
info: Hold Dumbel-Set in your hands with the palms facing each other. Pull your right hand toward your rib cage as you rotate to the right.

name: Abs Workout
info: A big misconception about training your abs is that it demands tons of time. The truth? You can effectively target your core by doing a bodyweight abs workout just a few times a week.

name: Legs Press
info: The leg press, a type of resistance training exercise, is an excellent way to strengthen your legs. It's done by pushing your legs against weights on a leg press machine.
